getDescriptionShort

public java.lang.String getDescriptionShort()
Each derived class should build a short description of themselves here using their type name and any other relevant class data. This string will be used to describe the item in the tree listview which has very limited screen space.

Returns:
Short description of this instance for use in the UI.
